    "title": {
      "rendered": "12 Nonprofit Call-to-Action Twitter Images to Study and Learn From"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Images-Facebook.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-18016\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Images-Facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Twitter Images Facebook\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Images-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Images-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Images-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Images-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Images-Facebook.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>It is true that <a href=\"http://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/photos-generate-engagement-research/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>tweets with images receive more engagement</strong></a>, but how much more engagement depends on the quality of the images and if they are properly sized for Twitter (<strong><a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/203154633168292810/\" target=\"_blank\">1024 \u00a0x \u00a0512 pixels or a 2:1 aspect ratio</a></strong>). If your nonprofit is committed to maximizing engagement on Twitter, then you must\u00a0create visually compelling call-to-action images for fundraising and advocacy campaigns. As we begin preparing for another year-end fundraising season spent tweeting and retweeting, studying the images below and creating a series of your own would be time and financial resources well spent.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a01. Sign online petition and pledges.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Extinction_OPS\" target=\"_blank\">@Extinction_OPS</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Extinction_OPS\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17961\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Pledge-2.png?resize=600%2C432\" alt=\"Twitter Image Pledge 2\" width=\"600\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Pledge-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Pledge-2.png?resize=300%2C216&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Make a donation.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/Survival\" target=\"_blank\">@Survival</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Survival/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17975\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Survival-International.png?resize=600%2C480\" alt=\"Twitter Image Survival International\" width=\"600\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Survival-International.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Survival-International.png?resize=300%2C240&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a03. Participate in a crowdfunding campaign.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/rainforesttrust\" target=\"_blank\">@RainforestTrust</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/rainforesttrust/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17966\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Fundraise-for-Us-2.png?resize=600%2C541\" alt=\"Twitter Image Fundraise for Us 2\" width=\"600\" height=\"541\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Fundraise-for-Us-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Fundraise-for-Us-2.png?resize=300%2C270&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Save the date and attend events.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/IndSector\" target=\"_blank\">@IndSector</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/IndSector/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17985\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Independent-Sector.png?resize=600%2C542\" alt=\"Twitter Image Independent Sector\" width=\"600\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Independent-Sector.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Independent-Sector.png?resize=300%2C271&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Enter a contest.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/GlblCtzn\" target=\"_blank\">@GlblCtzn</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/GlblCtzn/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17981\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Alley-Global-Citizen.png?resize=600%2C459\" alt=\"Twitter Image Alley Global Citizen\" width=\"600\" height=\"459\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Alley-Global-Citizen.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Alley-Global-Citizen.png?resize=300%2C229&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Take advantage of special promotions or sales.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/bestfriends\" target=\"_blank\">@BestFriends</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/bestfriends\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17993\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-best-friends-animal-society-2.png?resize=600%2C482\" alt=\"Twitter Image best friends animal society 2\" width=\"600\" height=\"482\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-best-friends-animal-society-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-best-friends-animal-society-2.png?resize=300%2C241&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a07. Apply for an internship or become a volunteer.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/hrc\" target=\"_blank\">@HRC</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/HRC/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17987\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-HRC.png?resize=600%2C497\" alt=\"Twitter Image HRC\" width=\"600\" height=\"497\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-HRC.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-HRC.png?resize=300%2C248&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Participate in hashtag campaign.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/OneCampaign\" target=\"_blank\">@OneCampaign</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/onecampaign\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17991\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-ONE.png?resize=600%2C482\" alt=\"Twitter Image ONE\" width=\"600\" height=\"482\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-ONE.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-ONE.png?resize=300%2C241&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Call\u00a0elected officials\u00a0(or socially irresponsible companies).<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/FeedingAmerica\" target=\"_blank\">@FeedingAmerica</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/FeedingAmerica\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17989\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Feeding-America.png?resize=600%2C479\" alt=\"Twitter Image Feeding America\" width=\"600\" height=\"479\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Feeding-America.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Feeding-America.png?resize=300%2C239&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Become a member.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/eff\" target=\"_blank\">@EFF</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/EFF\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17995\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-EFF.png?resize=600%2C491\" alt=\"Twitter Image EFF\" width=\"600\" height=\"491\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-EFF.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-EFF.png?resize=300%2C245&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. Complete an online survey or poll.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/PIRegistry\" target=\"_blank\">@PIRegistry</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/PIRegistry/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17963\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-PIR-Survey.png?resize=600%2C477\" alt=\"Twitter Image PIR Survey\" width=\"600\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-PIR-Survey.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-PIR-Survey.png?resize=300%2C238&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">12. Attend a webinar.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/AlleyCatAllies\" target=\"_blank\">@AlleyCatAllies</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/alleycatallies\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17979\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Alley-Cat-Allies.png?resize=600%2C468\" alt=\"Twitter Image Alley Cat Allies\" width=\"600\" height=\"468\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Alley-Cat-Allies.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Twitter-Image-Alley-Cat-Allies.png?resize=300%2C234&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2></h2>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
